Interface ExtractionContext.DatabaseObjectAccess

Enclosing interface:
ExtractionContext
@Incubating public static interface ExtractionContext.DatabaseObjectAccess
In conjunction with ExtractionContext.getDatabaseObjectAccess() provides access to information about known database objects to the extractor.
